Machinekit-HAL is continuation of work originating from Hardware
Abstraction Layer idea and code from Machinekit done by several
authors (inspectable at https://github.com/machinekit/machinekit),
which in itself is a fork of LinuxCNC project code (list of authors
can be examined at https://github.com/linuxcnc/linuxcnc)
is continuation of work based on the Enhanced Machine Controller, a
work of Fred Proctor, Tom Kramer, Will Shackleford, and others.

